  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Creating waste segregation awareness in Bangalore</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The recent problems with garbage disposal in Bangalore has made people realise the importance of waste management and segregation. The challenge now is that people are not aware of how to start segregating their household waste. This lack of knowledge is becoming a bottleneck to the solution for waste management in the city. Through this project we plan to spread awareness among people, including the domestic helps, on how to segregate the household waste correctly.</narrative>
  </description>
